      • getSelectionFormula

        java.lang.String getSelectionFormula()
        Generates a selection formula in format: SELECT Form = "myFormName" | Form = "myFormAlias" | Form = "myFormSecondAlias" etc.

        Continues for as many aliases as the Form has, not including aliases if none is defined.

        NOTE: Forms view in an NSF only displays the first alias of a design element, deisng element's properties box will shows all.

        Returns:
        String selection formula to access all Documents created with that Form
        Since:
        org.openntf.domino 3.0.0
